{"tid":1999500,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【選舉近了】熱狗四眼鄭錦滿 為選立會又玩分化","createTime":"2020-05-03T08:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T06:24:10.000Z","uid":103551,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b19970d665d14ef64c200cbbc5c2a1d146c47b93","tid":1999500,"uid":103551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿:<br />\n<br />\n接二連三有泛民議員協助政府監察人民，例如舉報有人觸犯「限聚令」、「限商令」，仲發展到協助差佬執法，監察返人民轉頭？<br />\n<br />\n同你哋討論咩係「民主」、「自由」都浪費時間，因為如果你哋識就唔會做以上行為，直接同你哋講「道義」！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你哋呢種行為及意識形態，已經得罪好多會落場「救手足」嘅車group朋友，我代佢哋發聲，因為你哋冇參與過，完全冇考慮佢哋感受！你哋對唔對得住手足？</span><br />\n<br />\n車group朋友希望我特別提醒你哋，搵個人企喺天橋影相、度分貝之類嘅工作，唔需要有議席嘅人先做得㗎，普通人有心做都可以，咪搵街坊輪班晚晚棟個人喺度囉，司機經過唔知咩事一定先減速。「議席」並唔係咁用！<br />\n<br />\n用「請投票，止警暴」、「五大訴求，一起公投」之類嘅說法呃咗個議席返嚟，發覺原來連喺區議會鬧差佬都唔得，民政會抽起文件唔畀討論，差佬會直接walk out甚至唔出席，處理唔到警暴問題，驚市民覺得自己做唔到嘢，所以要搵議題扮做嘢，甚至做埋差佬嗰份，協助暴政執法，監察人民，咪本末倒置啦！<br />\n<br />\n扮做嘢，搵其他工作喇，夏日炎炎去做滅蟲除草等清潔社區嘅工作，冇人會話你哋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bguv2qT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBguv2qT.jpg&h=76254d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">力數四眼三宗罪</span><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: orange;\">偷換概念</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">飛車黨</span>問題紮根已久，點會同近年出現嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">手足車</span>掛鈎？ 同埋呢幾日五一黃金週，日日凌晨兩三點係去邊到救手足？<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: orange;\">都係偷換概念</span><br />\n區議員<span style=\"color: orange;\">關注社區問題</span>，就變咗<span style=\"color: orange;\">協助暴政執法</span>，你咁唔滿意議員工作，咁你哋熱狗又走去選？<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: orange;\">口口聲聲手足前手足後，原來又係立會造勢</span><br />\n<br />\n搞咁大場龍鳳逐個逐個截圖，原來<span style=\"color: orange;\">嫌其他黃營議員擋你哋選立會條路，預先惡意分化</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HVjbg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HVjbg9.jpg&h=a11f0ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXfbMSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXfbMSq.jpg&h=4a6462bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RR3MAHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRR3MAHs.jpg&h=b28bd23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvaOO2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvaOO2C.jpg&h=4c547992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL9LRfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL9LRfS.jpg&h=49618ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主關注咗護士姐姐咁耐，真係睇唔過眼熱狗惡意抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9a7d4baf37a9706b89fc6255e3ac27eec95011","tid":1999500,"uid":46500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"食屎啦射撚滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9cb5b207754b9b5548bbd2445685182f3fb333","tid":1999500,"uid":103551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f9a7d4baf37a9706b89fc6255e3ac27eec95011","tid":1999500,"uid":46500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"食屎啦射撚滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"選舉近又咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137b43a76ab564555ed75822a54a1ba43724d5cc","tid":1999500,"uid":118520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"當日又簽確認書?"},{"pid":"b621bcb4733f974c657ec2c51664175c3e0a0fac","tid":1999500,"uid":249794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"當日四眼哥哥已經淪落到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢冇入熱狗唔知會唔會正常d<img src=\"/assets/